==Swedish==
===Noun===
plural of ''[[gris]]''

# [[pig]]

  [[gris]]  |  [[grisar]]             [[pig]] | pigs
 [[grisen]] | [[grisarna]]        the pig | the pigs

===Verb===
present of ''[[grisa]]'', most often in the expression ''[[grisa ner]]''

# Litterally: behave like a pig
# More commonly: make yourself or the area around you ''very'' dirty or messy. 

====Example====
A small child playing with its food, placing it everywhere in the kitchen (on the [[wall]]s/[[clothes]]/[[floor]]/etc...)